      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Member Luke$<BR>When you're on an adventure for a long time, sometimes you get lost and become confused on where to go and what to do. This means that you're experiencing a <FONT color=#a82424>slump</FONT> in your <FONT color=#a82424>adventure.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n341_guild_luke-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n341_guild_luke-2-b" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How do I get missions</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Member Luke${action:Talk}<BR>In those times, you can take <FONT color=#a82424>missions</FONT> from <FONT color=#a82424>Adventurer's Guild</FONT>. You will see an organized list of what you need to do or can do so you don't have to be worried about not knowing what to do.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n341_guild_luke-2-b" image="QW_WindForest.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n341_guild_luke-2-c" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What are missions?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Member Luke$<BR>At the areas outside town that is linked to the dungeons, you will see <FONT color=#a82424>Adventurer's Guild Bulletin Boards</FONT>. The nearest one from here is… <FONT color=#a82424>Wind Forest</FONT>. There is one Adventurer's Guild Bulletin Board in front of <FONT color=#a82424>Catacomb Entrance</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>Wind Forest Temple</FONT> each.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n341_guild_luke-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n341_guild_luke-2-d" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Member Luke$<BR>It is getting work that <FONT color=#a82424>matches your current abilities</FONT>. There are various missions from finding cats to killing monsters. Also, some boards have <FONT color=#a82424>Secret</FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>Quest</FONT> hidden inside.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n341_guild_luke-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n341_guild_luke-2-e" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay I will do that.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Member Luke${action:Talk}<BR>When you carry out <FONT color=#a82424>all the requests</FONT> in a bulletin board, a secret quest will be added. However, it is unknown which board has the hidden quest. Anyway... it'd be better to see for yourself. Try going there to take a look.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
